controlModulePackage
Class DevicesInfo

java.lang.Object
  controlModulePackage.DevicesInfo

public class DevicesInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a supportive class for the control module. The control module uses this class to store information of every devices that are instantiated and to track the status of the devices being connected and being displayed.

Author:
tianzhao

getAllPortsNames

public java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> getAllPortsNames()

startAllSignalDevices

public void startAllSignalDevices()
This function starts all the signal generator devices. We don't need a similar function for the measurement instrument devices because measurement instrument devices cannot generate data on its own. They must be connected to signal generators to get meaningful outputs.
